-- Rio Tinto says gets OK for Alcan offer
-- 
-- Thu Oct 18, 2007 9:59am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/18/us-riotinto-alcan-idUSWEN175420071018

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Anglo-Australian mining company Rio Tinto ( RIO.AX ) ( RIO.L ) said on Thursday it received all regulatory approvals required to close the $38.1 billion acquisition of Canada's Alcan AL.TO. 

 The $101 per share offer is set to expire on October 23, Rio Tinto said in a statement.